{"tid":1118314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女嬰遭蘋果砸中右腦失功能　家屬索償544萬人仔","createTime":"2019-04-21T10:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T08:58:13.000Z","uid":1121,"like":163,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"27b29b8d0e5e6823f7fae08415d17b3888503588","tid":1118314,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190421/photo/bkn-20190421114611227-0421_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190421123225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190421114611227-0421_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190421123225&h=a785a7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女嬰被蘋果砸中重傷，右腦喪失功能。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n廣東東莞一名時年3個月大的女嬰，去年3月由祖母抱着到寓所樓下散步時，突然遭從天而降的蘋果砸中頭部重傷。警方調查發現，蘋果原來是一名時年11歲的陳姓女童誤拋落街所致。女嬰家人將陳女和其家長告上法庭，索償逾544萬元人民幣（約646萬港元）。東莞市第三人民法院近日開庭審理該案，惟因雙方追加新被告，休庭擇日再審。 <br />\n<br />\n女嬰被砸中後腦部大面積出血，右側頭骨粉碎性骨折，傷勢嚴重。醫生表示，孩子創傷很嚴重，很難處理。雖已通過兩次手術顱內減壓，四肢面部稍為消腫，但孩子的右腦可能會喪失功能，過去1年曾先後入住深圳醫院兒科重症監護病房150次接受治療。 <br />\n<br />\n女嬰祖母表示，法醫鑑定女嬰重傷二級、十級傷殘，終生需家人照顧護理。當地警方成立了專案組調查事件，發現陳女事發時獨自一人在家。<br />\n<br />\n女嬰的余姓父親認為，陳女的家人應承擔全部賠償責任。惟陳家的代表律師認為索賠金額過高，並指屋苑開發商未有在公共場所設置防止物體墮落的措施，存在安全隱患，同樣有責任。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190421/photo/bkn-20190421114611227-0421_00952_001_02p.jpg?20190421123225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190421114611227-0421_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20190421123225&h=ff9b0efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女嬰受傷後不停出入醫院。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"3a6b6db1a8041f87c75fdf7b1fb1d6742f12c194","tid":1118314,"uid":1121,"like":692,"dislike":9,"score":683,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large/isaac-newton-and-the-apple-granger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.fineartamerica.com%2Fimages-medium-large%2Fisaac-newton-and-the-apple-granger.jpg&h=bad63212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3501f80325018f876ec87e4b355c8ff65f428cb","tid":1118314,"uid":1121,"like":576,"dislike":4,"score":572,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://freezerfananta.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/newton-and-apple.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreezerfananta.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F04%2Fnewton-and-apple.gif&h=6fb081e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b9b022e7933fb37155b0b93d97e8c4bbbe8b322","tid":1118314,"uid":49392,"like":562,"dislike":3,"score":559,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"BB頭骨同成年人頭骨比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfa0c0b5ee4e8179bc487844bc2121a71ade687","tid":1118314,"uid":149877,"like":249,"dislike":2,"score":247,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"錯的是地心引力"},{"pid":"57e03b623228062d3e5e5fe9d926eeddf472c7c9","tid":1118314,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec3de22e178bd638cba34fa4a6a91a70830ee08","tid":1118314,"uid":71657,"like":752,"dislike":8,"score":744,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"毁咗人成世 賠幾球嘢都話過高？"},{"pid":"671fe16de3efbeac80904f2e95d6124c028c7629","tid":1118314,"uid":35822,"like":204,"dislike":20,"score":184,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"全部都係牛頓發明地心吸力嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef300b68540ee9f2f4b6c7d881d81126bdc2d2a4","tid":1118314,"uid":84128,"like":286,"dislike":3,"score":283,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"並指屋苑開發商未有在公共場所設置防止物體墮落的措施，存在安全隱患，同樣有責任。 <br />\n<br />\n密封哂成個空間你咪扔唔到野落街"},{"pid":"3f1ca0757e208cecdbb5984191855e0135c9e370","tid":1118314,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"橙＞蘋果"},{"pid":"d5d8b005b0db6a40f78755a68d5